WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:05.350
The most, the most challenging part of my job is probably being able to

00:00:05.350 --> 00:00:09.850
 manage everything that's given to you without really fussing about

00:00:09.850 --> 00:00:14.350
 it. Some things you agree with, some things you won't agree with, and

00:00:14.350 --> 00:00:18.850
 you have to make sure that the part that you agree with, you know

00:00:18.850 --> 00:00:23.350
 you say it very, very clearly to your people. The parts that you don't

00:00:23.350 --> 00:00:27.850
 agree with, sometimes you have to actually tell your boss hey you

00:00:27.850 --> 00:00:32.350
 know what it's better this way, and whatever answer you get is whether

00:00:32.350 --> 00:00:36.850
 you know you can convince him or whether you have the materials

00:00:36.850 --> 00:00:41.350
 that it takes to convince him, otherwise you have to be strong in whatever

00:00:41.350 --> 00:00:45.850
 your convictions are and present it to your people. So it's

00:00:45.850 --> 00:00:50.350
 very good to take all of your input, everything that everybody's trying

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:54.850
 to tell you, and make sure that you understand it correctly and

00:00:54.850 --> 00:00:59.350
 that you can present it correctly. That's probably the most challenging

00:00:59.350 --> 00:01:03.850
 part of my job.

